name: CryptoGirl - 2021/Jan
description: CryptoGirl is a Universal men's lifestyle and entertainment magazine, formerly in fiat and currently in blockchain. It was founded by NSFNFT in 2021.  Notable for its centerfolds of nude and semi-nude CryptoPunks models, CryptoGirls played an important role in the NFT revolution and remains one of the world's best-known brands.
